= Page List View

Created by:  Andrew vonderLuft and Sean Cribbs, August 2008, in Portland Oregon

Enables viewing site pages in a list view sortable by attibute.

== Revision History

1.1 - 1/2009 - added pagination / full list options for CMSs with lots of pages
1.0 - 8/2008 - initial release

== Requirements

The will_paginate plugin

With the addition of pagination, you will need to add Mislav's will_paginate plugin to your vendor/plugins directory.  See http://github.com/mislav/will_paginate/tree/master
To install this plugin:
$ cd vendor/plugins
$ git clone git://github.com/mislav/will_paginate.git

== Installation

From your radiant root:

$ script/extension install page_list_view

Restart your radiant app, and you should be good to go.
   
